  m_text: "<size=150%><b><color=#FF7518>CREDITS</color></b></size><line-height=60%>\r\n<color=#B084F7>\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500</color>\r\n\r\n<size=120%><b><color=#FF7518>GAME
    DESIGN</color></b></size>\r\n<color=#F0E6D2><b>The T Virus & PsychGlow</b></color>\r\n\r\n<size=120%><b><color=#FF7518>PROGRAMMING
    & SOUND DESIGN</color></b></size>\r\n<color=#F0E6D2><b>The T Virus</b></color>\r\n\r\n<size=120%><b><color=#FF7518>CUSTOM
    3D MODELS / TEXTURES</color></b></size>\r\n<color=#F0E6D2><b>PsychGlow</b></color>\r\n<color=#F0E6D2>\r\nSanta
    Character  \r\t\t\t\tWitch Character  \r\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGhost Character  \r\nPriest
    Character  \r\t\t\t\tTeen Character  \r\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDoctor Character  \nNewspaper 
    \r\t\t\t\tCandy  \r\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBucket  \r\nCandy Bowl\r\n</color>\r\n<line-height=60%>\r<color=#B084F7>\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500</color>\r\n\r\n<size=130%><b><color=#FF7518>FREE
    / PAID ASSETS</color></b></size>\r\n<color=#F0E6D2>\r\n<b>House</b> \u2014 Elbolilloduro 
    \r\n<link=\"https://elbolilloduro.itch.io/house\"><u><color=#FFB347>https://elbolilloduro.itch.io/house</color></u></link>\r\n\r\n<b>PSX
    FPS Hands</b> \u2014 Niko_Gillsky  \r\n<link=\"https://niko-gillsky.itch.io/psx-fps-hands\"><u><color=#FFB347>https://niko-gillsky.itch.io/psx-fps-hands</color></u></link>\r\n\r\n<b>Gold
    Player</b> \u2014 Hertzole  \r\n<link=\"https://github.com/Hertzole/gold-player\"><u><color=#FFB347>https://github.com/Hertzole/gold-player</color></u></link>\r\n\r\n<b>Trees
    PSX</b> \u2014 Elbolilloduro  \r\n<link=\"https://elbolilloduro.itch.io/trees-psx\"><u><color=#FFB347>https://elbolilloduro.itch.io/trees-psx</color></u></link>\r\n\r\n<b>Retro
    PSX Nature Pack</b> \u2014 Elegant Crow  \r\n<link=\"https://elegantcrow.itch.io/retro-psx-nature-pack\"><u><color=#FFB347>https://elegantcrow.itch.io/retro-psx-nature-pack</color></u></link>\r\n\r\n<b>Low
    Poly Car - BMW E46 1998</b> \u2014 ROH3D  \r\n<link=\"https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/low-poly-car-bmw-e46-1998-d9bfd8126e754164b48ded833c017bbf\"><u><color=#FFB347>Sketchfab
    Link</color></u></link>\r\n\r\n<b>PSX Female Secretary Character</b> \u2014 Vinrax 
