  goodDialogue:
  - textList:
    - Ho-ho-ho!
    - Looks like we still got some trick or treaters!
    - Here, take this!
  - textList:
    - Ho-ho-ho!
    - Don't look so glum!
    - You're on the nice list this year.
  - textList:
    - Here you go!
    - Just promise me you'll leave some milk and cookies out for me.
  badDialogue:
  - textList:
    - Out this late?
    - Only naughty kids skip their curfew.
    - Why don't you take this.
  - textList:
    - "You don\u2019t look like you believe in me."
    - "That\u2019s\u2026 disappointing."
    - It's coal for you this year, little kid.
  - textList:
    - Saint Nick has a trick for you my little elf.
    - "Take this and don\u2019t tell Mrs. Claus I\u2019m handing these out."
